quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,71,"O maaki: "…ďee …óoo ko jiw…ďe am, si wonii ko on wa…óoo…ďe [go…ó…óum]!""
  15,72,"Mi woondirii nguurndam maa! …ďe ngonii e siwrugol ma…ď…ďe he…ďe mbeemi."
  15,73,"Haacaango ngoon nanngiri …ďe ka pu…óal,"
  15,74,"Min mb…ótiniri dow mayre on ley mayre, min saa∆īini(to…ďri) e ma…ď…ďe kaa∆īe iwru…óe e loope ju…óaa…óe."
  15,75,"Wonii e …óuum, maandeeji wonan¬īde …ďen teskotoo…ďe."
  15,76,"Pellet, …óeen [ca'e] no e jurol(bolol) √Īii…ďngol."
  15,77,"Wonii e …óuum, maande wonan¬īde …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  15,78,"GooŇč…óii yim…ďe fitaare(sutu) …ďeen [kadi] ko too√Ī…ďe."
  15,79,"Min yo…ďtii e ma…ď…ďe. Pellet …óeen [ca'e] …ói…ói ngonii e laawol …ďanngungol."
  15,80,"GooŇč…ói yim…ďe (aynde) Hijiri nden njeddii nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  15,81,"Min ngaddani …ďe aayeeje amen …óen, …ďe laatii …óuurnii…ďe …óe."
  15,82,"Hari he…ďe lesoynoo e pelle …óeen cuu…ói, ko …ďe hoolii…ďe."
  15,83,"Haacaango ngoon nanngi …ďe ka subaka."
  15,84,"Nafaani…ďe …óuum ko …ďe laatinoo he…ďe paggitoo."
  15,85,"Min tagiraani kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, si wonaa e goonga. Pellet, darngal ngal ko arayngal! yaafora jaafaggol labaangol."
  15,86,"Tabitii ko Joomi maa woni Tak…óo, ganndu…óo."
  15,87,"GooŇč…óii min okkii ma jee…ói…ói ummorde …óimmitaa-ngol, e Alqur'aanaare mawnde nden."
  15,88,"Wata a …ďamtu gite maa …óen e neemaaji …ói lin dakmiti …ďe e mum en, wata a sunu e ma…ď…ďe, les…óin becce maa …óen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  15,89,"Maaku: "min ko mi jertinoowo …ďannginoowo"."
  15,90,"Wano min njppinirnoo e senndoo…ďe [defte Alla] …ďen [lepte],"